These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, indie
1. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | country | house | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | hedgehog | guinea-pig | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, car, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | car | subway | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, singing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | board-games | singing | hiking |

 #################################

 
