.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery | time-travel |

 #################################

 
